{
  "id": "RAW_93a980b8",
  "title": "10B 击败 200B！阶跃星辰 10B 视觉语言 SOTA 模型开源",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNTYxNzg5Mg==&mid=2247486886&idx=1&sn=c9789eec18f250735b8868a1f9dc3a5d",
  "date": "2026-01-20 09:30:00",
  "author": "阶跃星辰",
  "siteName": "阶跃星辰",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=81f500b7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F0LDJQiaWfxznPPYwVX0aW0FGBbp2fn8hGEMib7KKeKyCIxO81ybohUlLKicCyFTGX0o2drlopmtQ6oqic0hvj4F4zA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">性能超越 20 倍大模型，阶跃星辰多模态“小核弹”&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;\">Step3-VL-10B</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">开源！</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"1440\" data-imgfileid=\"100003216\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"2560\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8fd6d860&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0LDJQiaWfxznPPYwVX0aW0FGBbp2fn8hGAgDvQnP1CwNp1pic3D85cTEEMk1KgoqkdWwsx16tia66f7SAiaCZNedWg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">仅用 10B 参数量，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;\">Step3-VL-10B 在视觉感知、逻辑推理、数学竞赛以及通用对话等一系列基准测试中均达到同规模 SOTA 水平</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，并且解决了参数量小和智能水平高难以兼优的行业难题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们在多项关键评测中观察到，Step3-VL-10B 媲美甚至超越规模大 10-20 倍开源模型（如 GLM-4.6V 106B-A12B、Qwen3-VL-Thinking 235B-A22B）以及顶级闭源旗舰模型（如 Gemini 2.5 Pro、Seed-1.5-VL）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">基于这样一个小而强底座，原本只能在云端运行的复杂多模态推理（如 GUI 操作、复杂文档解析、高精度计数）能够下沉到手机、电脑甚至工业嵌入式设备中。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;\">Base 和 Thinking 模型同时开源，欢迎下载体验！</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">项目主页：<a href=\"https://stepfun-ai.github.io/Step3-VL-10B/\" target=\"_blank\">https://stepfun-ai.github.io/Step3-VL-10B/</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">论文链接：<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2601.09668\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2601.09668</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">HuggingFace：<a href=\"https://huggingface.co/collections/stepfun-ai/step3-vl-10b\" target=\"_blank\">https://huggingface.co/collections/stepfun-ai/step3-vl-10b</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">ModelScope：<a href=\"https://modelscope.cn/collections/stepfun-ai/Step3-VL-10B\" target=\"_blank\">https://modelscope.cn/collections/stepfun-ai/Step3-VL-10B</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <h2 data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:40px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 98, 255);font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">10B参数，200B性能</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Step3-VL-10B 具备三大核心亮点：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: square;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">极致视觉感知标杆</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在同参数量级中展现出顶尖的识别与感知精度。通过引入&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">PaCoRe（并行协调推理）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;机制，模型在复杂计数、高精度 OCR 及空间拓扑理解等高难度任务上的可靠性实现了质的飞跃。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">深层逻辑推演与长程推理</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">得益于规模化强化学习（RL）</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">的持续迭代，Step3-VL-10B 在 10B 规模上实现了跨任务推理能力的阶跃。无论是竞赛级数学难题、真实编程环境还是视觉逻辑谜题，模型均能通过严密的</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">多步思维链推导出最终答案。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">强大端侧 Agent 交互</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">基于海量&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">GUI</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">（图形用户界面）专用预训练数据</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，模型能够精准识别并操作复杂界面，成为端侧 Agent 的核心引擎。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;margin-top: 16px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Step3-VL-10B&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">提供&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">SeRe</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">（顺序推理）和&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">PaCoRe</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">（并行协调推理）两种范式，在STEM 推理、识别、OCR &amp; 文档、GUI Grounding、空间理解、代码等核心维度，都取得了千亿级别模型的优秀分数，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;margin-top: 16px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">PaCoRe范式表现更优。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">1、STEM /多模态推理</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">STEM（科学、技术、工程、数学）与多模态推理（Multimodal Reasoning）是衡量模型“深度智能”的核心维度。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Step3-VL-10B 在 MMMU、MathVision 中超越 GLM-4.6V、Qwen3-VL 等模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100003232\" data-ratio=\"0.9583333333333334\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4c68d22e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0LDJQiaWfxzklnRH4tvd3jYwTUUG1jBWeTjAbAA6dxZnaG95Xfjcz0gq2evYPEQbRhkFuLFuoEY1uGtr3cxfTMQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">2、竞赛数学</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在数学维度上，Step3-VL-10B 表现尤其突出。在 AIME 25/24 等数学竞赛测试题上以几乎满分的成绩达到世界第一梯队水平。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这意味着 Step3-VL-10B 已具备了顶尖人类数学竞赛选手的思维能力，在逻辑严密性上甚至优于许多千亿级模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100003233\" data-ratio=\"0.6259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3843f79a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0LDJQiaWfxzklnRH4tvd3jYwTUUG1jBWefW9sRNUJe24DfA1Ub3BvzJIuNYwMA20whu88FUtmjdd3I6Tt8KbDrA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">3、2D/3D空间推理</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">Step3-VL-10B 在多个空间推理基准中都表现出优异水平，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">尤其是在需要精细感知与复杂逻辑结合的&nbsp;</span></span><b data-path-to-node=\"1\" data-index-in-node=\"52\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">BLINK、CVBench、OmniSpatial 及 ViewSpatial</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;等测试中，其性能显著超越了同规模模型。</span></span></p>\n  <div>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.0425925925925925\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100003237\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e9bc7993&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0LDJQiaWfxzklnRH4tvd3jYwTUUG1jBWefv7TRyoLiaqDnoibWcn9FhwtET8TVWYBL9nAymvOq9BzIctUiccwib6AIQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">4、代码</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在真实、动态编程环境下，Step3-VL-10B 超越诸多世界一流多模态模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.2916666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100003235\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f3f48012&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0LDJQiaWfxzklnRH4tvd3jYwTUUG1jBWe9H9ED5AeEt49bruR25UumG4dutYV3ibfkG0eqibh0LSO3Gjz6dapxeXQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:40px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 98, 255);font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">真实案例</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在真实使用场景中，Step3-VL-10B 的多模推理能力覆盖 GUI 感知、视觉识别和推理等。</span></span></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">案例一：莫尔斯推理</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <div style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;overflow-y: auto;height: 300px;width: 677px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;line-height: 0;visibility: visible;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100003224\" data-ratio=\"1.2638888888888888\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4471fce5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0LDJQiaWfxznPPYwVX0aW0FGBbp2fn8hG5OphhhxSMyuXUqmcF47s3PfFQ6vqVXIVyX4tlsxThtvy0WGpN6aYPw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(160, 160, 160);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:12px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 16px 0px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-align: center;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">▲上下滑动查看详细内容</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">案例二：GUI 感知</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <div style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot