width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 16px 0px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-align: center;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">▲上下滑动查看详细内容</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">案例三：图推理</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <div style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;overflow-y: auto;height: 300px;width: 677px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;line-height: 0;visibility: visible;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100003226\" data-ratio=\"1.0851851851851853\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bfed0d1f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0LDJQiaWfxznPPYwVX0aW0FGBbp2fn8hGWEzoFnAibqY6oS26IlticbCFric3kTO76c9yriab6R1LaEtq0RvR7TKohQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(160, 160, 160);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:12px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 16px 0px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-align: center;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">▲上下滑动查看详细内容</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <h2 data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:40px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 98, 255);font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">为什么能做到？三项关键设计</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">能够达到以上性能，得益于 Step3-VL-10B 在三方面独特设计：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">1.全参数端到端多模态联合预训练</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">摒弃了传统分阶段冻结模块的训练范式，直接在 1.2T 高质量多模态数据集上进行全参数联合训练。这种方式实现了视觉特征与语言逻辑在底层语义空间的深度对齐，为模型构建了极致的感知能力与复杂的跨模态推理基石。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">2.大规模多模态强化学习（RL）演进</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">率先将大规模强化学习引入多模态领域，历经超过 1,400 次迭代优化。模型在视觉识别、数理逻辑推理及通用对话等维度的能力均实现质的飞跃，且实验数据表明，模型性能仍处于上升通道，尚未触及饱和边界。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">3.并行协调推理机制（PaCoRe）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">创新性地引入 PaCoRe 机制，支持推理阶段的动态算力扩展。通过并行探索多个感知假设并进行多维证据聚合，该机制显著提升了模型在竞赛级数学、复杂 OCR 识别、精准物体计数及空间拓扑推理中的准确度。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">得益于“三位一体”架构，Step3-VL-10B 证明智能水平并不完全取决于参数规模。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">依托更高质量、更有针对性的数据构建，以及系统化的后训练与强化学习策略，</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">10B 级模型同样有能力在多项基准测试中与 10–20 倍体量的模型正面竞争，甚至实现反超</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这也意味着：</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">世界一流的多模态能力有望以更低成本、更少算力获得</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">；与此同时，过去主要集中在云端超级智能将逐步</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">向端侧下沉</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，推动终端走向“主动理解与可执行交互”，从而重塑人机交互体验。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">目前，我们已开源 Step3-VL-10B（包括 Base 模型和 Thinking 模型），欢迎大家与我们讨论交流，也欢迎开源社区来微调我们的模型，共同推动小模型实现智能跃迁！</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "阶跃星辰开源了 10B 参数的视觉语言模型 Step3-VL-10B，通过 PaCoRe 机制和大规模强化学习，在多项基准测试中性能媲美甚至超越 200B 级模型。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "阶跃星辰开源了 10B 参数的视觉语言模型 Step3-VL-10B，通过 PaCoRe 机制和大规模强化学习，在多项基准测试中性能媲美甚至超越 200B 级模型。",
  "summary": "阶跃星辰正式开源其多模态大模型 Step3-VL-10B，包含 Base 和 Thinking 两个版本。该模型仅凭 10B 参数量，在视觉感知、逻辑推理、数学竞赛及通用对话等基准测试中达到同规模 SOTA 水平，部分指标超越了 GLM-4.6V (106B) 和 Qwen3-VL (235B) 等千亿级模型。核心技术突破包括：全参数端到端多模态联合预训练、历经 1400 次迭代的大规模多模态强化学习（RL），以及创新性的并行协调推理机制（PaCoRe）。该模型的开源标志着高性能多模态能力向手机、电脑等端侧设备下沉的可能性，显著降低了复杂 AI 任务的算力成本。",
